Name: Camlock Pp Type A Male Adaptor X Female Bsp 40mm
Short_description: Camlocks are a kind of hose coupling used to rapidly connect and disconnect fittings on piping or hoses.
Description: Camlocks also called cam and groove couplings, are a kind of hose coupling used to rapidly connect and disconnect fittings on piping or hose, they come in a variety of materials to be used with different media and a variety of sizes to accommodate hose or piping diameter.Camlock connectors are capable of carrying liquids, powders and granules and are interchangeable with all other cam and groove couplings made to the same standard (A-A-59326A – formally MIL-C-27487), [1] ensuring compatibility with couplings made to the same specification.PP TYPE A, has a male camlock end and a female pipe thread (BSP or NPT thread) of the same size.\nWhat's in the box\n1 x Camlock Pp Type A Male Adaptor X Female Bsp 40mm

Description: Camlocks also called cam and groove couplings, are a kind of hose coupling used to rapidly connect and disconnect fittings on piping or hose, they come in a variety of materials to be used with different media and a variety of sizes to accommodate hose or piping diameter.Camlock connectors are capable of carrying liquids, powders and granules and are interchangeable with all other cam and groove couplings made to the same standard (A-A-59326A – formally MIL-C-27487),[1] ensuring compatibility with couplings made to the same specification.PP TYPE F, has a male camlock end and a male pipe thread of the same size.\nWhat's in the box\n1 x Camlock Pp Type F Male Adaptor X Male Bsp 100mm

Name: Camlock Pp Type E Male Adaptor X Hose Tail 100mm
Short_description: Camlocks are a kind of hose coupling used to rapidly connect and disconnect fittings on piping or hoses.
Description: Camlocks also called cam and groove couplings, are a kind of hose coupling used to rapidly connect and disconnect fittings on piping or hose, they come in a variety of materials to be used with different media and a variety of sizes to accommodate hose or piping diameter.Camlock connectors are capable of carrying liquids, powders and granules and are interchangeable with all other cam and groove couplings made to the same standard (A-A-59326A – formally MIL-C-27487),[1] ensuring compatibility with couplings made to the same specification.PP TYPE E, has a male camlock end and a male hose tail on the other.\nWhat's in the box\n1 x Camlock Pp Type E Male Adaptor X Hose Tail 100mm

Description: Camlocks also called cam and groove couplings, are a kind of hose coupling used to rapidly connect and disconnect fittings on piping or hose, they come in a variety of materials to be used with different media and a variety of sizes to accommodate hose or piping diameter.Camlock connectors are capable of Carrying liquids, powders and granules and are interchangeable with all other cam and groove couplings made to the same standard (A-A-59326A – formally MIL-C-27487),[1] ensuring compatibility with couplings made to the same specification.PP TYPE B, has a female camlock end and a male pipe thread of the same size.\nWhat's in the box\n1 x Camlock Pp Type B Female Coupler X Male Bsp 100mm
